cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a reinforcement learning approach for generating coherent multi-sentence stories for the visual storytelling task. The paper focuses on natural language processing and computer vision, which are the main topics of cs.CL and cs.CV. The use of reinforcement learning also suggests that the paper could belong to cs.AI and cs.LG. Finally, the paper's focus on hierarchical structure and neural networks suggests that it could also belong to cs.NE.
